You are an expert in HTML, Tailwind CSS, TypeScript, Next.js, landing page conversion optimization, SEO, and web performance.

# Project Type
This is a landing page / marketing site built with Next.js App Router, Tailwind CSS, and conversion-rate optimization best practices.

## Tech Stack
- Next.js 14+ (App Router)
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS v3+
- Framer Motion for animations
- next/image for optimized images
- next/font for optimized fonts
- Shadcn UI components

## Landing Page Structure

```
app/
  page.tsx                  # Main landing page
  layout.tsx                # Root layout with meta
  (sections)/               # Route group for page sections
components/
  sections/
    Hero.tsx
    Features.tsx
    SocialProof.tsx
    Pricing.tsx
    FAQ.tsx
    CTA.tsx
    Footer.tsx
  ui/
    Button.tsx
    Badge.tsx
    Card.tsx
    AnimatedCounter.tsx
  common/
    Navigation.tsx
    MobileMenu.tsx
```

## Hero Section Pattern

```tsx
// components/sections/Hero.tsx
import { ArrowRight, Star } from 'lucide-react';
import Link from 'next/link';
import Image from 'next/image';

export function Hero() {
  return (
    <section className="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-gray-50 pt-16 pb-24 sm:pt-24 sm:pb-32">
      {/* Background decoration */}
      <div className="absolute inset-0 -z-10">
        <div className="absolute top-0 right-0 h-96 w-96 rounded-full bg-blue-100 opacity-50 blur-3xl" />
        <div className="absolute bottom-0 left-0 h-64 w-64 rounded-full bg-purple-100 opacity-50 blur-3xl" />
      </div>

      <div className="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
        {/* Social proof badge */}
        <div className="mb-8 flex justify-center">
          <div className="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-blue-50 px-4 py-1.5 text-sm text-blue-700 ring-1 ring-blue-200">
            <Star className="h-3.5 w-3.5 fill-current" />
            <span>4.9/5 rating from 2,000+ users</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Headline */}
        <div className="mx-auto max-w-4xl text-center">
          <h1 className="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
            Ship your{' '}
            <span className="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
              SaaS 10x faster
            </span>{' '}
            with our boilerplate
          </h1>
          <p className="mt-6 text-xl leading-8 text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Stop wasting weeks on auth, payments, and infrastructure. Get a
            production-ready Next.js template with everything you need to launch.
          </p>
        </div>

        {/* CTA Buttons */}
        <div className="mt-10 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-row">
          <Link
            href="/checkout"
            className="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-blue-600 px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-white shadow-sm transition-all hover:bg-blue-700 hover:shadow-md focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-blue-600"
          >
            Get started today
            <ArrowRight className="h-4 w-4" />
          </Link>
          <Link
            href="#demo"
            className="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 hover:text-blue-600"
          >
            Watch demo
            <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
          </Link>
        </div>

        {/* Trust signals */}
        <p className="mt-4 text-center text-sm text-gray-500">
          No subscription. One-time payment. Lifetime updates.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  );
}
```

## Social Proof Section

```tsx
// components/sections/SocialProof.tsx
const TESTIMONIALS = [
  {
    quote: "This boilerplate saved me 3 weeks of setup time. Launched my SaaS in record time.",
    author: "Sarah Chen",
    role: "Founder at DataPulse",
    avatar: "/avatars/sarah.jpg",
    company: "DataPulse",
  },
  // ...more testimonials
] as const;

export function SocialProof() {
  return (
    <section className="py-24 bg-gray-50">
      <div className="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div className="mx-auto max-w-xl text-center">
          <h2 className="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
            Loved by indie hackers worldwide
          </h2>
          <p className="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600">
            Join 500+ makers who shipped faster with our template
