## File Naming Conventions

- Sections: `PascalCase.tsx` in `components/sections/`
- Pages: `page.tsx` (Next.js convention)
- Static data: co-locate with component or in `data/[name].ts`

## What Cursor Should Do

- Add `priority` to hero images (LCP optimization)
- Generate Open Graph metadata for all pages
- Use semantic HTML (section, article, figure, figcaption, dl/dt/dd)
- Add ARIA labels and roles for accessibility
- Implement Schema.org structured data for products
- Use `next/font` for Google Fonts
- Generate CTA with clear value propositions

## What Cursor Should Avoid

- Do NOT use `<img>` — use `next/image`
- Do NOT use Google Fonts CDN — use `next/font`
- Do NOT use Lorem Ipsum — suggest real placeholder content
- Do NOT use generic button text ("Click here") — use action verbs
- Do NOT skip mobile optimization — always use responsive Tailwind classes
- Do NOT forget `alt` text on all images
- Do NOT use `target="_blank"` without `rel="noopener noreferrer"`
